items.title: Black Air
items.description: The Air & The Nike React Vision are a story of surreal comfort. Layered textures, shapes and vivid colours are combined in a design influenced by the exaggerated world of our dreams, while React foam and an ultra-plush tongue provide surreal comfort. DIMSIX on the tongue tab rises high off the collar to add just a touch of Nike's own origin story.
